verbose_text: These results indicate HIF-lalpha only promotes lung cancer proliferation under hypoxia, whereas survivin expression vector transfection in HIF-lalpha knockdown cells partly revived proliferation under hypoxia (XREF_FIG).
evidence: HIF-lalpha only promotes lung cancer proliferation under hypoxia, whereas survivin expression vector transfection in HIF-lalpha knockdown cells partly revived proliferation
